006package gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.databind.model.metaschema.binding;
007
008import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.model.IBoundObject;
009import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.model.IMetaschemaData;
010import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.databind.model.annotations.MetaschemaAssembly;
011
012import org.apache.commons.lang3.builder.ReflectionToStringBuilder;
013import org.apache.commons.lang3.builder.ToStringStyle;
014
015@SuppressWarnings({
016    "PMD.ShortClassName",
017    "PMD.FieldNamingConventions" })
018@MetaschemaAssembly(
019    formalName = "Any Additional Content",
020    name = "any",
021    moduleClass = MetaschemaModelModule.class)
022public class Any implements IBoundObject {
023  private final IMetaschemaData __metaschemaData;
024
025  public Any() {
026    this(null);
027  }
028
029  public Any(IMetaschemaData data) {
030    this.__metaschemaData = data;
031  }
032
033  @Override
034  public IMetaschemaData getMetaschemaData() {
035    return __metaschemaData;
036  }
037
038  @Override
039  public String toString() {
040    return new ReflectionToStringBuilder(this, ToStringStyle.MULTI_LINE_STYLE).toString();
041  }
042}
